    <body>

      

      <div type="description" n="monument" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>A <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="catMonument">plaque</rs> (<measure type="length" dim="height">0.295</measure> × <measure type="length" dim="width">0.53</measure> × <measure type="length" dim="depth">0.04</measure>), with the back left rough; chipped at
upper and lower edges.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>Inscribed on the face; the initial <foreign lang="grc">Σ</foreign> of <foreign lang="grc">Στέφανος</foreign> was cut above the
line.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Av. <measure type="length" dim="height">0.02-0.025</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0600" exact="none" notBefore="0401">Fifth/sixth century</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">metre</rs>).</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head lang="eng">Edition</head>
     <lg met="dactylic hexameter" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
	  	<lb n="1"/>
	  <l n="1" part="N"><mark type="cross"/> <w lemma="σῆμα" part="N">σῆμα</w> <w lemma="ὅδε" part="N">τόδε</w> <persName key="stephanus4" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Στέφανος">Στεφάνοιο</name></persName> <w lemma="ὁ" part="N">τὸν</w>
	  	<lb n="2"/><w lemma="ἐν" part="N">ἐν</w> <w lemma="ζωός" part="N">ζωοῖσιν</w> <w lemma="ἀκούω" part="N">ἀκούεις</w></l>
	  	<lb n="3"/>
	  <l n="2" part="N"><w lemma="εὐσεβής" part="N">εὐσεβίης</w> <w lemma="γίγνομαι" part="N">γεγαῶτα</w> <w lemma="διάκτορος" part="N">διά
		<lb n="4" type="worddiv"/>κτορον</w> <w lemma="ἤπιος" part="N">ἤπιον</w> <w lemma="ἀνήρ" part="N">ἄνδρα</w></l>
		<lb n="5"/>
	  <l n="3" part="N"><w lemma="ἀκμή" part="N">ἀκμὴν</w> <w lemma="εἰς" part="N">ἐς</w> <w lemma="βίοτος" part="N">βιότοιο</w> 
	  	<lb n="6"/><w lemma="ὁ" part="N">τὸν</w> <w lemma="ἁρπάζω" part="N">ἥρπασε</w> <w lemma="λοίμιος" part="N">λοίμιος</w> <persName key="fate" type="divine" full="yes"><w lemma="αἶσα" part="N">αἶσα</w></persName> <mark type="cross"/></l>
	  </lg>
      </div>

      

      <div type="translation" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab part="N">This is the grave of Stephanus, whom you hear among the
living to have been a servant of piety, a gentle man; in the prime of
life the doom of disease snatched him away.</ab>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" evaluate="all" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" from="ROOT" n="IX.20">IX.20</xref>, and,
for verse inscriptions, <xref type="eAla-text" evaluate="all" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" from="ROOT" n="IX.15">IX.15</xref>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations" part="N" sample="complete" org="uniform"><head>Locations</head><p>Found: <rs type="findspot">Fields: at Palamucuk, north of Aphrodisias.</rs>. Original location: <rs type="orig-location">Unknown.</rs>. Last recorded location: <rs type="last-location">Museum.</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

